Program: The Why Factor
Title: Dogs
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cswrjz
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 4 Jun 2018
Why do we have such a close and complex relationship with dogs? No matter whether you love or hate them, it’s undeniable they’ve built up a special relationship with us that most animals haven’t. On this episode of The Why Factor, we find out why dogs are so special. Mary-Ann Ochota delves into the emotion, science and history that sets them apart - be they friend, foe or food. (Image: Essex Search and Rescue, Credit: Gabriela Jones/BBC) Show less